yTime":"2021-02-05T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"探肛準啲？"},{"pid":"949a05a7aa2a6f0b21cc2819449dbda36dedcbb9","tid":2396220,"uid":1191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"男醫生拎條龍出黎不停檢驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be30d83e0df223ab4457a43d111e148c6de1cbc8","tid":2396220,"uid":279124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"仲可以去到旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d826ea6b4721f199d97d981972fb171cc5ad7e92","tid":2396220,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"使狗國者，從狗門入。"},{"pid":"7f33acb10fb88d7301b58538ae33d28f57d48ffd","tid":2396220,"uid":3748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"某南韓人入境中國時。檢疫員說要肛門採樣。他脫褲子彎腰，當醫生把棉花棒塞入肛門時，他痛得掉下眼落。塞藥後，醫生囑咐：<br />\n&ldquo;這些棉花棒，每三天要測多一次，十四日後即可。&rdquo;<br />\n當晚，某男讓老婆幫忙。老婆明白用藥方法後，一手搭在他肩膀上，另一隻手把棉花棒塞入他肛門。<br />\n男人大罵：&ldquo;該死！&rdquo;<br />\n老婆問：&ldquo;弄疼你啦？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;一點都不痛，我剛想起來，早上檢疫員是兩手搭在我肩上&hellip;&rdquo;"},{"pid":"57ea074652c456a1a9752578e7a5b4918097b86c","tid":2396220,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb2afd9bfaa5b3c40050c1f87651e7c9db0062","tid":2396220,"uid":222238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKffxzx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%